[h4 id=Randomness 
	" Randomness
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"The only randomness that matters with King Hippo is him opening his mouth.  There is a 6/16 chance of him opening his mouth for any given punch.  This is determined by the lower nibble of the RNG address (0x0018).  If this nibble is 01, 03, 06, 09, 0B, or 0E, he will open his mouth.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Thus the odds of getting the correct randomness to get the fastest possible time is a 6/16 * 6/16 * 6/16.  This reduces to a 27/512 to approximately a 5% chance.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"If given perfect execution and average randomness, a player will on average beat King Hippo between 0:55 and 1:00
	$LF
]p
